name: Personalized Pink Polka Dot Tutu Tote Bag
description:
~This tote makes a great dance bag, diaper bag, or school bag.

This adorable tutu tote bag measures 13.5" x 13.5" x 3" with 14" handles, a bottom gusset and is made of sturdy canvas. The tutu is hand-made from pink, black and white layers of tulle and then sewn on the tote along with the ribbons and bows. The bows on top can also be worn as hair ribbons (they have an alligator clip). The ballet slippers applique is included next to the name. 

FREE personalization~ Please include the name in the notes on the PAYPAL order form.

Please allow 5-7 business days for production
